data.description: Nestled in the heart of Mattoon, this sought-after ranch-style home is the one you are looking for.    Inside, you will find an amazing floor plan and updates throughout.  Engineered hardwood flooring adorning the eat-in kitchen and laundry areas. You will also appreciate the spacious pantry cabinetry, conveniently located just off the kitchen.    The primary bedroom, featuring an en suite bathroom, offers a large private retreat within this homes spacious layout. An open floor plan creates seamless transitions between living spaces, with a brick fireplace surround in the family room, adding warmth and character to gatherings.    Pride of ownership shines through every corner of this home, evident in the care and attention given to its upkeep.  Many updated bath fixtures throughout the house are just one example of the homeowners dedication to keeping this home in meticulous condition for it's new owner.    A delightful surprise awaits with the bonus room adjacent to the garage, equipped with water and air conditioning. Once a darkroom for photo processing, this versatile space opens up a world of possibilities for your creative endeavors or functional needs.    Outside, a large patio provides plenty of space for entertaining or simply relaxing, while the remarkable 12x18 sunroom adds not only a focal point for the entire home, but a touch of luxury that floods the home with natural light.
